text: Sergio Tesitore (born 10 February 1967) is a Uruguayan former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Uruguayan male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Uruguay Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Canelones Department
